node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021 tagging @jaredoks. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks Over the last 3 years I've made over $15M in sales with my eCommerce businesses. Here is how did it. (A thread)'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks In my 2nd year of college got introduced to eCommerce. saw some of my friends having success with it, so decided to try myself. was a broke college student and just wanted to make some extra money.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared oks started multiple dropshipping stores tried it all -Dropshipping cheap products -Building brands from scratch -Making viral ads heard Basically all the strategies everyone talk about, but none of it really worked for me.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_ok lost every dollar in my bank account and even got into debt starting all those businesses and made no profit. But was determined to make eCommerce work and in my 3rd year of college, came across high ticket dropshipping.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jar_ realized the potential of selling expensive products( $1000+) from the US suppliers, using Google ads and without ever needing to buy buy inventory.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks decided to give eCommerce one more try. spent all my free time, even the breaks between classes, building my business. was contacting suppliers, building stores, looking for products, answering customer questions, etc.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_ _oks And it paid off. 8 months later, month. was making $10K per Even before graduated from college| hit a 6-figure income with my dropshipping stores.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks Over the last 3 years, I've made over $15M in online sales and built 5 eCommerce businesses. I've then used that money to invest in real estate stocks, and crypto.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks Throughout my journey learned that the way to succeed in eCommerce is to: -Sell high ticket products -Use U.S. suppliers -Use Google ads -Have great customer support'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_ok So this is the story of how started my journey as an entrepreneur. Folow me if you'd ike to learn more about eCommerce, I'm sharing lots of value daily about what learned from building my eCommerce businesses.'.

node.text:
This is the power of compound interest!

Buffett didn't make most of his wealth until he was well into his 30s. But Buffett was never in this for the money...he wanted the independence. He made it BIG from long term investing alone, and anyone can do that.

Dividends, bonds, ETF's, real estate, etc...there are so many options and opportunities to make it BIG. GET TO WORK.

Follow us @businessinstantly
